sections.heading: Conveyances; claims and improvements upon public lands; law applicable
sections.text: Sections 76-201 to 76-281 and 76-2,126 apply to the conveyance of all claims and improvements upon the public lands.SourceR.S.1866, c. 43, § 35, p. 287;R.S.1913, § 6231;C.S.1922, § 5630;C.S.1929, § 76-236;R.S.1943, § 76-277;Laws
